headline: Teledyne to Participate in the Baird Global Industrial Conference
summary: THOUSAND OAKS, Calif., November 10, 2025--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) today announced that George Bobb, President and Chief Executive Officer, and Jason VanWees, Vice Chairman, will hold investor meetings at the Baird 2025 Global Industrial Conference on Wednesday, November 12.
